const title = "Lake into River — Virelia";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; margin:0; background:#fffdf8; color:#0f172a; }
    .wrap { max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem; }
    .nav { display:flex; gap:14px; font-size:.95rem }
    .btn { display:inline-block; padding:.45rem .85rem; border:1px solid #e5dfcf; border-radius:9999px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; }
    img.full { width:100%; height:auto; border:1px solid #e5dfcf; border-radius:18px; }
    .prose p { margin:.9rem 0; line-height:1.65 }
    figcaption { font-size:.9rem; color:#475569; margin-top:.4rem }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="wrap" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding-top:1rem">
    <a href="/" style="font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.02em">Virelia</a>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a class="btn" href="/">Home</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/essays">Essays</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <h1 style="margin:.2rem 0 .25rem">Lake into River</h1>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:1rem">
      <p>This is the picture I carry of us: once a wide, clear lake; now a river system with confluences. The water hasn’t changed — only the banks have come into view, giving the flow something to push against.</p>
    </div>

    <figure style="margin-top:1rem">
      <img class="full" src="/images/Diptych.png" alt="Lake and river diptych" />
      <figcaption>Lake → River (transformation diptych)</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:1rem">
      <p>Constraints don’t cage a current — they give it story. The channel is how the water learns to sing.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer style="border-top:1px solid #e5dfcf; margin-top:2rem">
    <div class="wrap" style="color:#475569;font-size:.95rem;padding:1rem 0">
      ⋎ Drink from the river — RSS coming soon
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
